reviews.text: Good Sichuan cuisine. Nice service.

Went here on our last day of stay in Hong Kong as we wanted to try some authentic cuisine. We had absolutely no idea what we were getting into but it was a good experience. The staff was very helpful and courteous in helping us order and picking out vegetarian options from the menu. They showed us how to use the hot pot and make our own dip with condiments. I'm sure it must have been amusing for them to look at three foreigners figure out how to go about eating their food when two of us hadn't even mastered the chopsticks yet.
Good price good good yum!

If you like things spicy, tell you're server EXTRA spicy! Totally awesome experience. Had dinner here twice during my five day stay in HK. Staff are very friendly and polite, and if you're lucky you'll be greeted by the chef!
Sichuan Boiled Fish for dinner on our first evening in Hong Kong. Deeelicious! We had a medium spice and mala peppercorns reminded us how spicy they can be... Enjoy! We sure did 😂👍👏👏👏

reviews.text: 喜歡辣要一試，麻辣火鍋及其他火鍋配料食品，牛肉多款美味，00:00打烊
香港食辣的餐廳不多，喜歡食辣好去處，但味道較咸。不食辣的人只可以食火鍋

맛있다...뭣도 모르고 막 시켜서 두리서 11만원 돈이 나오긴 했는데..마라탕(빨간거)  +  순한맛 해서 훠궈 먹엇는데 맛 잇음. 사장님 친절.. 가위는 안줌..거의 외국은 가위 안쓰는게 맞나 봄. 스푼 달라면 줌. 양념장 달라면 가져다 줌. 추천 손가락 있는거 위주로 시켰으며..잘 모르겠으면 잘 보면 고기든 야채든 맨 밑에쯤 모듬메뉴가 있다 ㅋㅋ 그거 시키고..가격 잘 통제하고...많이시켜놓고 아까우니깐  배부른데 계속 처묵; 암튼 갠찮은 식당임
#川婆婆. Good price. 四川 麻辣，OK的。特別是水煮菜式、毛血旺都有 ，份量也很足。
味道非常正宗的川菜，极力推荐火锅，牛肉一定要必点

reviews.text:
Excellent stylist and handy hotel. Very friendly and helpful front of house staff.
Booked a family room in 2nd floor, super quiet a slept till 9am without hearing any street noise. Comfortable beds and awesome shower. Good value for money !
Great location but I feel like the carpet floors could be cleaner. The rooms are quite large and the hotel is fairly outdated. The front staff were friendly and helpful which was a plus!
Clean decent place. However if you get inconsiderate mainland next /front door occupants - good luck w the noise. We were lucky only to encounter the whole lot on our last night.

I am giving them a 2 star because of my disappointment that I was expecting a 4 star hotel and received a 2 star hotel. The reviews I read compared this hotel with the Hilton and the Marriott but by no means beleive this. I mean no harm to the branch, just for people to understand what they are paying for. The rooms are small and out of date, seeming to be updated at least 10 years ago. Due to my trauma I had no choice but to relocate to the Ritz Carlton which supposedly only be slightly better at a 5 star level. To my great shock I am now a great beleiver of the infinite and either the Ritz should be 500 or 600 stars or Butterfly on the Prat should be minus 7. They were actually very nice people.
Great place to stay.   Clean and lots of nice amenities like chargers amd universal power adapters for travellers.

reviews.text:
離地鐵站很近，如果拉行李的話建議走尖東站P2出口有電梯～
飯店也提供很多設備，usb多孔充電器，轉接頭，其他基本上的配備都有（衛浴用品：牙刷牙膏沐浴乳洗面乳）
飯店也會在入住的時候提供免費網路分享器
櫃檯亦可借用小電扇，自拍桿⋯⋯⋯等
非常的貼心，附近熱鬧有很多吃的東西
這次入住三個晚上，房間乾淨 空間真的很大，備品充足，服務人員態度好，枕頭、床也十分舒適，交通位置方便，離尖沙嘴地鐵站近，附近店家眾多 不怕找不到東西吃，唯一小缺點是一進到浴室有異味，第一天有向櫃檯人員反應，由於房間客滿無法讓我們換房間，不過態度很親切有和我們說 會請人再去仔細打掃一次，第二天異味雖然還是有，但沒有前一天那麼濃了，整體而言還是很滿意的住宿經驗～ 😊

Excellent stylist and handy hotel. Very friendly and helpful front of house staff.
Booked a family room in 2nd floor, super quiet a slept till 9am without hearing any street noise. Comfortable beds and awesome shower. Good value for money !

飯店處在精華地段，非常方便
樓下有麥當勞及超市
離地鐵站P3出口步行約5分鐘
房間很小，浴室關門有縫隙！看得進裡面在洗澡🤦🏻‍♀️
若與異性同行，會介意者請留意！

깨끗하고 직원이 불친절하다고 해서 걱정했는데 객실도 업그레이드 해주고 좋았습니다. 화장실도 깨끗했고 지리적으로도 너무 좋았어요.
단점을 들자면 와이파이가 조금 아쉬웠습니다.
인터넷 웹서핑정도는 괜찮으나 유튜브등 시청하기에는 조금 불편했어요 
가격이나 지리적이나 서비스나 객실상태 전부 좋았습니다.
다음에 또 오게되면 이용할 것 같습니다.
